   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting effective safeguards for prisoners&apos; rights during pre-trial detention</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to tackle the use of forced confession and other forms of ill-treatment during criminal pre-trial detention in China&apos;s criminal justice system through a pilot project working with the police bureau in Yunnan Province in China. It is expected that the project will provide a frame of reference for further amendments to the Criminal Procedure Law in China.</narrative>
